\par\plain {\f0\fs22\b0\i0\cb3\highlight3 ACIM }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\super\cb3\highlight3 2}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cb3\highlight3  The course does not aim at teaching the meaning of love, for that is beyond what can be taught. It does aim, however, at removing the blocks to the awareness of love's presence, which is your natural inheritance. The opposite of love is fear, but what is all-encompassing can have no opposite.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs22\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 The course does not aim at teaching the meaning of love, for that is beyond what can be taught.\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8221\'94 If we search the Urantia Book for a definition of love we see that it references the Thought Adjuster (a fragment of God living within us, the purest most indestructible form of reality) as the greatest manifestation of diving love. }{\f0\fs22\b0\i0 Since Adjuster is the greatest manifestation of divine love, we can connect the dots and determine that love and the god fragment that lives within us is beyond our ability to understand. We can however, experience this infinite reality.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs22\b0\i0 UB 2:5.10 The greatest manifestation of the divine love for mortal beings is observed in the bestowal of the Thought Adjusters, but your greatest revelation of the Father's love is seen in the bestowal life of his Son Michael (Jesus) as he lived on earth the ideal spiritual life. It is the indwelling Adjuster who individualizes the love of God to each human soul.}
\par\plain \f0\fs22\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93It does aim, however, at removing the blocks to the awareness of love's presence, which is your natural inheritance.\u8221\'94 In Urantia Book terms I read this to mean the course aims at removing the blocks to the Thought Adjusters presence. This course is the result of the life Jesus lived in the flesh. }
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
